---
title: Chicken Cacciatore with Mushrooms and Fusilli
description: Cacciatore, Italian for “hunter’s stew”, gets its namesake from a common method of preparing wild game. In this recipe, juicy chicken thighs are simmered in a rustic tomato sauce and served with hearty fusilli pasta.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-cacciatore-30fc4ede.jpg
